gGb(){return"I learn how to pick my own lock!\n\nMy own test lock\n\nMy own transparent test lock..."},
gGa(){return"Make Liquors"},
gG9(){return"Technically, according to chemistry, alcohol is a solution"},
gFZ(){return"Attack Networks"},
gFY(){return"I learnt how to enter in a wireless network.\n\nWas pretty easy since I already knew the password..."},
gG4(){return"Edit Photos"},
gG3(){return"I started editing some pictures to make people more beautiful or funny.\n\nI think I failed with myself..."},
gGe(){return"Travel"},
gGd(){return"Mountains, lakes, forests... Yeah, Google Maps is really cool"},
gG2(){return"Chess"},
gG1(){return"I like to challenge whoever wants to play chess.\nSo I play with myself...\n\nAnd sometimes I even win!"},
gG8(){return"Kickboxing"},
gG7(){return"Everyone has a plan until they get punched in the mouth\n(Mike Tyson)"},
gGi(){return"Volleyball"},
gGh(){return"Volleyball and beach volley are sports I really like.\nAnd I play them with all people I can find\n\nLast game was in 2017..."},
gFX(){return"Airsoft"},
gFW(){return"The pen is mightier than the sword. But the gun is mightier than the pen"},
gGg(){return"Video Games"},
gGf(){return"I like several video games such as fps, arpg, mobas, mmos, mmorpgs, etc.\nBut I still have a social life!\n\nI exit at least once a month!"},
gG0(){return"Card Games"},
gG_(){return"I like several card games like Scopa, Briscola, Poker and others.\nI'm a gambler!\n\nOnce I even played a game for 5 euros!"},
